custom_minimum_size = Vector2(100, 0)
layout_mode = 2
text = "Enemies are the colored triangles characters that you will see chasing you down. They will try to get close to lend a hit on you, so be careful!
They are separated in 3 groups by color, RED, BLUE and GREEN. 
They can only be efficiently harmed by the right colored weapon/bullet, for example, a RED enemy is only harmed by RED weapons/bullets.
You can kill all enemy types with any weapon type, but it will take a greater amount of bullets.
As the waves go on, they will be more numerous, faster, and more diverse, so use the time between the waves to heal and find new items that might aid you."
